build instructions

1. change version in cache.manifest
2. change version*Code* in config.xml
3. compile Release
4. change iOS PhoneGap key to Production (latest date), Android key to UrbanAsk
5. turn off Debug build on PhoneGap
6. upload urbanask.zip file to PhoneGap
7. download Android and iOS binaries and save to /builds

iOS
8. copy urbanask.zip to Dropbox/Projects/urbanAsk/www and unzip
9. open in Xcode, click on urbanAsk project in sidebar, target urbanAsk, Summary tab, change Version
10. In Xcode, click on Resources/urbanAsk-Info.plist in sidebar, change Bundle version
11. Click on Resources/AirshipConfig.plist in sidebar, change APP_STORE_OR_AD_HOC_BUILD to YES
12. Compile app: Project menu, Archive
13. If not already open, open Organizer (Window menu, Organizer)
14. click latest archive, select Distribute, then iOS app store
15. add new version at iTunes Connect
16. send binary using Application Loader

Android
8. run android zipalign on .apk file
9. upload to Amazon and Google Play

